REPORT yctproba5.

DATA: rem TYPE p DECIMALS 2.


PARAMETERS: number type i.


START-OF-SELECTION.

rem = ( number MOD 2 ).


IF rem EQ 0.
  WRITE: / 'Even'.
ELSE.
  WRITE: / 'Odd'.
ENDIF.
